# WRITE A PROGRAM THAT WILL DISPLAY THE FOLLOWING QUESTIONS FOR USER:
#       “WHAT IS YOUR NAME?“
#        “HOW OLD ARE YOU?“
#        “WHERE DO YOU LIVE?“
# and will read the user's responses and display the corresponding messages:
#       “HELLO, (ANSWER(NAME))“.
#       “YOUR AGE IS  (ANSWER(AGE))“.
#       “YOU LIVE IN  (ANSWER(CITY))“.   

user_name = input ("What is you name? \n" )
user_age = input ("How old are you? \n")
user_location = input ("Where do you live? \n")

print(f"""
Hello, {user_name}
Your age is {user_age}
You live in {user_location}
""")